data.description:
Impressive views from this 1-story 3BR, 2.1BA Pool home in All-age 24/7 gated community of Winston Trails.  Spacious, meticulously maintained designer home features 11' ceilings, tile & luxury vinyl flooring, hi-hat lighting, newer light fixtures & fans, crown molding & plantation shutters. Custom kitchen boasts Quartz countertops, beautiful hardwood cabinets, SS appliances w beverage cooler.  Formal living, dining room and family room off of the kitchen.   Spacious Primary Suite enjoys NW exposure, view of pool and 16th Green.  Renovated bath w double vanities, frameless shower & free-standing soaking tub.  Split bedroom plan w 2nd & 3rd BR's that share upgraded 2nd Bath. Remodeled cabana bath & laundry room w extra storage. Fully fenced back yard w low maintenance enjoys refreshing solar & electric heated pool, open patio, retractable electric awning, bistro lighting, remarkable sunsets and scenic fairway views to adjacent lake.   Tile Roof 1996, Solar Panels, A/C 2018, Wtr Htr 2016, Accordion Shutters, New pool motor.  Basic cable & internet included in Low Hoa Fee.  Pet Friendly!

Winston Trails non-equity golf course community featuring Clubhouse, Café/Restaurant, Tennis, Lakes, Playgrounds, & Sidewalks throughout the community. Short driving distances to parks, beaches, casual & fine dining, entertainment & shopping. Enjoy some of the best golf in your own community.  Easy access to Turnpike, I-95 and short drive to Palm Beach Int'l Airport.
